=======================================================================
nkMedia v.1.0


REQUIREMENTS

- Apache2
- PHP5
- Icecast2
- libssh2


INSTALLATION

1. Download the sources

git clone https://github.com/neokinok/experimentaltv

2. Fix folder permissions

   chmod 777 log 
   chmod 777 mediabase -R
   chmod 777 lib/itheora/data -R

3. Create a database and import SQL

  mysql -uUSERNAME -pPASSWORD DATABASE_NAME < admin/sql/mediabase.sql

4. Change configuration.php file, updating your database preferences



